{"tid":2439244,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彩虹旗飄揚 「不想走回頭」","createTime":"2021-03-09T06:12:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T07:07:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bacfa9df7f4e94f9738c0b4ba5af67391565a6d8","tid":2439244,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T06:12:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210309/5NWDI2TP4RFH5MZPNFT6RA4C3U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210309%2F5NWDI2TP4RFH5MZPNFT6RA4C3U%2F&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhyy9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=83bbd06f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210309%2F5NWDI2TP4RFH5MZPNFT6RA4C3U%2F&h=2cd186d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210309/5NWDI2TP4RFH5MZPNFT6RA4C3U/</a><br />\n<br />\n彩虹旗飄揚 「不想走回頭」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OiEJNihZErQBOJoQVy2ZK480_YQ=/802x467/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LDWI23REW5DI3CKFUIVS4IZP2A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOiEJNihZErQBOJoQVy2ZK480_YQ%3D%2F802x467%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLDWI23REW5DI3CKFUIVS4IZP2A.jpg&h=524c7da1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■緬甸性小眾在近年始被接受，全拜民選政府包容。<br />\n<br />\n「就算我們這些性小眾大部份都不會有子女，我們也要為後人着想，為以後所有性小眾抗爭！」緬甸同志李傑（音譯，Jel Li）不諱言上街是因為「我們已不想走回頭路」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：國際專題：縫隙中傳真相 fb直播抗爭  緬游擊記者 守住數碼前線<br />\n<br />\n緬甸全國由最大城市仰光到中部城鎮瑞波，近日掀起了浪接浪的大規模反軍政變示威，在各地飄揚的全國民主聯盟紅色旗海下，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n緬甸是保守的佛教國家，社會傳統本來對非異性戀者並不友善，加上繼承了英國的殖。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：英語文宣 盼國際關注支援<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與軍政府難談包容<br />\n<br />\n可是上月初的政變，令緬甸性小眾有唇亡齒寒之憂，他們擔心爭取了十幾年的平權努力會付諸東流，緬甸性小眾團體「多色彩虹」副主任侯妙墩（音譯，Hla Myat Tun）坦言：「我們好不容易才走到這裏。」跟一言堂的軍方談包容，無疑是天方夜譚，因此政變對緬甸性小眾來說，是一場重回地下與上街抗爭之間的抉擇。<br />\n<br />\n瑞波一名同性戀者顯然。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n路透社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/q4mI6iPYpaAOCvwbMtpeBklIaJo=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FIMHOPHTUNCQVNTGSNOTH5IXUU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fq4mI6iPYpaAOCvwbMtpeBklIaJo%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFIMHOPHTUNCQVNTGSNOTH5IXUU.jpg&h=ab9dd783&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■一向保守的緬甸自開放以來，性小眾得以走上平權路，他們表示不願走回頭路。"},{"pid":"564883eca7956118487aaf22908ee6703658e737","tid":2439244,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T07:05:55.000Z","msg":"香港走得好前 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Untitled-1-0720copy_mKrF8_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FUntitled-1-0720copy_mKrF8_1200x0.png&h=e7e4d6e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"071070e1e7f22dd863dc408723f4cf942a008315","tid":2439244,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T07:07:46.000Z","msg":"連登係同性戀最大平台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}